Key Match Events: Sadio Mane scored a 96th-minute winner from a 25-yard free-kick to seal Senegal's 1-0 win over Malawi and a place at the Africa Cup of Nations finals in Morocco next year
Miscellaneous Highlights: Senegal had 30 attempts at goal against Malawi but only managed a single goal
Ghana are in serious danger of missing out on the Africa Cup of Nations finals after a surprise loss to Sudan
Others: Democratic Republic of Congo qualified for the Africa Cup of Nations finals with a 2-0 victory in Tanzania
Coach Avram Grant's Zambia claimed an important 1-0 win over Chad to take a big step towards qualification
Gabon are also on course after a 2-0 win over Lesotho in neutral Durban
